{"tid":1610734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港第二個孫中山就係梁天琦","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:45.000Z","uid":92836,"like":75,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e989608f2ecafbafc93d0c67ebd2d7e57cd5f325","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:31:31.000Z","msg":"1894年 ，孫中山向李鴻章上一本萬言書，<br />\n仲講梗一個滿政府去點樣改革。<br />\n<br />\n1895無人理孫中山 成立咗興中會正式嘅革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等於2014啟發梁天琦嘅雨革，認為香港還有得救，於2015加入而本民前。啟動時代革命嘅序幕<br />\n<br />\n1984年嘅萬言書想滿清政府改革 = 2016年新東補選嘅宣言<br />\n<br />\n1895年嘅乙未廣州起義 = 2016年正式嘅魚革響起警示。<br />\n第一次革命雙方都有犧牲(陸皓東被捕犧牲，梁天琦黃台仰李東昇全部被捕)<br />\n<br />\n孫中山亦被通緝 = 梁天琦選舉後無得入閘<br />\n(當時仲孭梗官司)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">本民前 =興中會(未來或會有新政黨)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">梁天琦=國父</span><br />\n<br />\n本民前嘅策略<br />\n留下梁天琦受審<br />\n黃台仰 李東昇用德國人權大國去增加國際曝光關注<br />\n就係為之後革命嘅路鋪下<br />\n當梁天琦出翻黎嘅時候<br />\n就係港共政權跪低之時。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後續嘅我唔分析了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNA0W2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNA0W2S.png&h=070e76c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=1db00b24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n孫中山革命都用咗29次先成功一共用咗16年<br />\n梁天琦都講革命係一條長嘅路，保持呢個革命嘅精神<br />\n<br />\n呢個夢想要繼續保持希望去繼續去做。"},{"pid":"8b8db5e5aff8e8d3e5645e049124386ac9a90093","tid":1610734,"uid":130194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee51b845b85ce94702b6f7f1e2d44fc18f06229","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:33:28.000Z","msg":"所以李嘉誠個有錢佬就係睇準邊便就泊岸了"},{"pid":"3aa3fa933fa02813d7c9904151c0ec58c451aafc","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"依加個階段 係時代革命<br />\n下一個階段就係光復香港"},{"pid":"dbe5d97e206066bbdd6b841c367128960dd55a2e","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:36:41.000Z","msg":"依加同以前比較就係爭咗國際輿論戰線同武裝起義"},{"pid":"d2bf7d13f226aaaf53dbab619814b7a881faa393","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e98f523c2b1eeed93e95815b0b975727564f0f89","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"16e146c072d647cdcadc26f99528923090cccb2f","tid":1610734,"uid":150935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:40:27.000Z","msg":"我愛天琦一生一世"},{"pid":"01e37775a5c46be4f5ff2d3b3709591a9560f2b1","tid":1610734,"uid":215755,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:40:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XoS1bwsUfnw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXoS1bwsUfnw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=5632c363\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XoS1bwsUfnw</a><br />\n<br />\n本民前好多成員仲參與緊"},{"pid":"e3cf5e43a9cc966a675201f8ac2ac08e40aaf4ad","tid":1610734,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:41:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n必須武裝起義<br />\n01/10/2019<br />\n係一個新開始"},{"pid":"e2d63bd131c8b4c278c22ac2a1463a6b417f856b","tid":1610734,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"天崎未安全"},{"pid":"777452ca873c30386ff4a3a35e2170f94f115bfe","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:45:05.000Z","msg":"&quot;但其實革命本身係一樣乜野事呢<br />\n革命本身就係講緊一個社會結構<br />\n權力分配<br />\n一個根本性既改變,一個從下而上既改變<br />\n一個從上而下既改變,其實係代表一個改革<br />\n而一個從下而上既改變就係革命<br />\n咁大家諗下今時今日<br />\n你地仲會唔會奢求<br />\n中國 香港特區政府<br />\n從上而下 改革<br />\n仲會唔會相信佢地會俾我地有民主<br />\n俾我地有自由<br />\n冇可能<br />\n所以話<br />\n我地必須要革命&quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢段說話出自梁天琦既發言<br />\n而「光復香港，時代革命」呢句口號係由梁天琦開創既<br />\n<br />\n我地諗一諗,「五大訴求,缺一不可」係一個從上而下既改變,定還是係從下而上既改變<br />\n我相信係前者,因此呢句口號講緊既係訴求,係要中央,特區政府點頭,答應,實行<br />\n<br />\n矛盾就出現係到,<br />\n大家追求既係改革定還是革命?<br />\n<br />\n革命,需要既唔係訴求,而係推翻政權"},{"pid":"3d8a64508fd8d37aea2577bb7dbdd444f6fcc2cc","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d63bd131c8b4c278c22ac2a1463a6b417f856b","tid":1610734,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"天崎未安全"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:53:06.000Z","msg":"如果因為呢一個post令到天琦喺監倉內有生命安全<br />\n我願意刪post同埋全部連登仔會一齊出嚟搶犯"},{"pid":"2343cd80370a350b0666aa3292cfdf11a44436cd","tid":1610734,"uid":193233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:56:15.000Z","msg":"推！我地要真革命啊！"},{"pid":"d22ef022b2bc9abf3d75abc9c781748f036c1e78","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2343cd80370a350b0666aa3292cfdf11a44436cd","tid":1610734,"uid":193233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:56:15.000Z","msg":"推！我地要真革命啊！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:00:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推多幾野"},{"pid":"5e438782ec0a54688e1a0a19bb878492a38101eb","tid":1610734,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aW3U1Rn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaW3U1Rn.gif&h=2dedcd0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ceee8990af86fdba365d833595d1b020843092f","tid":1610734,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e438782ec0a54688e1a0a19bb878492a38101eb","tid":1610734,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:05:14.